Core
====
 + A user should be able to create a note(title, body).
 - A user should be able to view a list of saved notes.
 - A user should be able to view the complete note(title, body) when he clicks on the title in the list page.
 - A user should be able to delete a note.
 - A user should be able to edit a note.

Nice to have
============
 - A user should see a confirmation before a note is deleted
 - A user should not be able to create a note without a title

 - Deploy the app


